## Task 2: OllamaEngine — InferenceEngine for Ollama

### Step 1: Write failing test

Create `crates/corvia-kernel/src/ollama_engine.rs` with just the test:

```rust
#[cfg(test)]
mod tests {
    use super::*;
    use crate::traits::InferenceEngine;

    #[test]
    fn test_ollama_engine_dimensions() {
        let engine = OllamaEngine::new("http://localhost:11434", "nomic-embed-text", 768);
        assert_eq!(engine.dimensions(), 768);
    }
}
```


### Step 2: Run test to verify it fails

Run: `cargo test -p corvia-kernel -- test_ollama_engine`
Expected: FAIL — `OllamaEngine` not defined
